<A>__{on a big screen tv in a private banquet room, the springbok team watches the england all black semi final, which the all blacks dominate from beginning to end thanks to the exploits of jonah lomu, their unnaturally huge, fast left wing, of tongan parentage (and unanimous choice for the best player in the entire world cup). jonah lomu scores in the first two minutes of the match, the first of four tries. he runs through, over, and around hapless defenders. his speed and balance are almost unprecedented in a man his size. the springboks go quiet as they watch this beating by the all blacks.}
